products.description: What it is: A manicure set featuring everything you need for the perfect salon-quality gel manicure from the comfort of your home.What it does: The 3-in-1 gel polish combines base coat, color and top coat all in one bottle and cures in 30 seconds with the Le Mini Macaron LED lamp. The glossy, nonsticky, 9-free formula lasts up to 7–10 days with two coats or up to 3 weeks with three coats. The powerful, macaron-shaped lamp works for pedicures too; just flip the magnetic top around.Set includes:- LED lamp with USB cord (3 watts, 0.77 oz., 2" x 1.3")- One bottle of gel polish in a matching color (0.29 oz.)- Cuticle stick- Mini nail file- 10 remover wraps- Detailed instructionsHow to use: File the edge and surface of your nails. Use nail polish remover and wipe away the dust and oils. Apply a VERY thin (barely there) layer of gel polish. Cure in the LED lamp for 30 seconds. Apply a second layer of gel polish, and cure again. And that's it—you're done. For a perfect removal, file the surface of your gel manicure that you wish to remove. Tear open the remover pad and insert your finger, with the cotton pad over the nail. The acetone from the cotton pad will soak into the gel. Wrap the packet around your finger, removing the sticker on the packet to ensure that it’s air-tight. Wait 15 minutes. Remove the packet and the gel polish will have a shattered effect. Use the cuticle stick to scrape off the gel.
